# this is a comment (started by the hash character '#'); empty lines are ignored as well
# the format of this file is as follows:
# each line (unless it is a comment) contains:
# 1. a list of (comma-separated) words, 
# 2. a tab character '\t', and  
# 3. a list of (comma-separated) AVPairs.
# AVPairs marked by their attribute, followed by a colon ':', followed by the value
# Greifarm Example:
hoch	size:big,location:top
gro√ü,grosz, gross	size: big
lang	size : big
kurz	size :small
# the following line (when uncommented) should lead to an error (redefinition)
